  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://ollama.com/assets/library/llama3-groq-tool-use/ebf53e82-1faf-4bac-84b0-47b8f5d9d8d1\" width=\"240\"/></p>\n\n<p>These models, developed in collaboration with <a href=\"https://glaive.ai/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Glaive</a>, represent a significant advancement in open-source AI capabilities for tool use/function calling.</p>\n\n<h2>Benchmark Results</h2>\n\n<p>These models have achieved remarkable results, setting new benchmarks for Large Language Models with tool use capabilities:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Llama-3-Groq-70B-Tool-Use: 90.76% overall accuracy (#1 on BFCL at the time of publishing - July 2024)</li>\n<li>Llama-3-Groq-8B-Tool-Use: 89.06% overall accuracy (#3 on BFCL at the time of publishing - July 2024)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Groq\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugging Face</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wow.groq.com/introducing-llama-3-groq-tool-use-models/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blog</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
